item.title: Use `console.log()` Like a Pro
item.description: I saw this tweet the other day and left it aside to read it later. Use `console.log()` Like a Pro: https://t.co/amWg5HbO2p — JavaScript Daily (@JavaScriptDaily) December 1, 2020 I won’t lie to you, I don’t code a lot. I code as less as possible. My associate is way better than me and it’s just not really my thing. But I still deal with a lot of code for projects and I have to understand it.
